ch, email sequences, and follow-ups autonomously.\n \nFounders using it get 10-15 hours/week back and go from a couple conversations a week to 15+ in 60 days.\n \n14-day free trial, no credit card. Want me to send the link?", "Quick case study that might resonate:\n \nOne founder spent $398 on SAM and generated $50K in pipeline in 60 days. No SDR. No agency. Just the AI running in the background while he focused on product.\n \nHappy to share the full breakdown if helpful.\n", "Last thought and I''ll leave you alone:\n \nThe math most founders face:\nâ†’ SDR: $70K/year + 3 months to ramp\nâ†’ SAM: $199/month, starts working day one\n \n15 min to walk through it: https://calendar.app.google/L9wG3XkUnWnDZJQ17", "No worries if timing isn''t right.\n \nWe built a free GPT that helps founders build their outbound playbook â€” ICP definition, messaging sequences, pipeline math. Figured it might be useful regardless.\n \nhttps://links.innovareai.com/OutboundGPT\n \nRooting for {company_name} either way."]', '{}', NULL, '{}', NULL, '{"email_body": "", "email_body_b": "", "initial_subject": "", "initial_subject_b": "", "ab_testing_enabled": false, "connection_request": "Hi {first_name}, came across {company_name} and was curious about what you''re building. Always looking to connect with early-stage founders â€” happy to be a resource if useful.", "follow_up_messages": ["Thanks for connecting. Finding early customers while you''re still building is brutal. Most founders I talk to are stuck doing it all themselves â€” no time to prospect, too early to hire. Curious if that''s your world too.\n", "We built something that might help â€” SAM, an AI agent that runs LinkedIn outreach, email sequences, and follow-ups autonomously.\n \nFounders using it get 10-15 hours/week back and go from a couple conversations a week to 15+ in 60 days.\n \n14-day free trial, no credit card. Want me to send the link?", "Quick case study that might resonate:\n \nOne founder spent $398 on SAM and ge