nerated $50K in pipeline in 60 days. No SDR. No agency. Just the AI running in the background while he focused on product.\n \nHappy to share the full breakdown if helpful.\n", "Last thought and I''ll leave you alone:\n \nThe math most founders face:\nâ†’ SDR: $70K/year + 3 months to ramp\nâ†’ SAM: $199/month, starts working day one\n \n15 min to walk through it: https://calendar.app.google/L9wG3XkUnWnDZJQ17", "No worries if timing isn''t right.\n \nWe built a free GPT that helps founders build their outbound playbook â€” ICP definition, messaging sequences, pipeline math. Figured it might be useful regardless.\n \nhttps://links.innovareai.com/OutboundGPT\n \nRooting for {company_name} either way."], "follow_up_subjects": [], "alternative_message": "", "connection_request_b": "", "use_threaded_replies": false, "alternative_message_b": ""}', '471bcb15-cc53-44f3-b5d2-4b97bb7a8b2f', '{"enabled": true, "end_time": "17:00", "timezone": "America/Los_Angeles", "start_time": "05:00", "business_days": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5], "allow_weekends": false}', '2025-11-28 12:11:04.031+00', true, 'America/New_York', 7, 18, true, true, 'US', '{"messages": {"goodbye": "Alright, last message from me. I''ll assume outbound automation isn''t a priority right now.\n\nBeing a founder is chaosâ€”I get it. Wishing you the best with {company_name}.\n\nIf things change down the road, feel free to reach out.", "follow_up_1": "Hi {first_name}, great to connect.\n\nSo here''s what we do: We built an AI agent called Sam that handles outbound prospecting end-to-end. Finds leads, sends messages, follows up, drafts replies.\n\nMost founders I talk to are either spending 10+ hours a week doing this themselves, or they''re paying $70K+ for an SDR they can''t really afford yet.\n\nWe helped one B2B SaaS company go from 2 demos a week to 15 in about 60 days. No extra headcount.\n\nHow are you handling outbound right now?", "follow_up_2": "Hi {first_name}, great to connect.\n\nSo here''s what we do: We built an AI agent called Sam that handles outbound prospecting end-to-end. Finds leads, sends messages, follows up, drafts replies.\n\nMost founders I talk to are either spending 10+ hours a week doing this themselves, or they''re paying $70K+ for an SDR they can''t really afford yet.\n\nWe helped one B2B SaaS company go from 2 demos a week to 15 in about 60 days. No extra headcount.\n\nHow are you handling outbound right now?", "follow_up_3": "Not sure if outbound is on your radar right now, but figured I''d mention this:\n\nWe''ve got a 14-day free trialâ€”no credit card, no commitment. You tell us who you''re targeting, Sam handles the outreach, and when people reply, you get a draft response in 15 minutes.\n\nWorth trying, or is this just not a priority for you right now?", "follow_up_4": "Last thing from me on this.\n\nHere''s the math:\nAn SDR costs you $70K/year plus 3 months to ramp.\nSam costs $199/month and starts working immediately.\n\nWe''re running tiered pricing right now: $99/month for the next 20 signups, then it jumps to $119, then $139, until we hit full price at $199. Currently 14 spots left at $99.\n\nDoes this make sense for where you''re at, or am I totally off base?", "follow_up_5": "Just making sure you saw thisâ€”we''re down to 8 spots at $99/month. Once these are gone, it moves to $119 for the next tier.\n\nIf you''ve been thinking about the outbound problem, this is probably the easiest (and cheapest) way to solve it.\n\nThoughts?", "connection_request": "Hi {first_name}, \n\nI work with early-stage founders on scaling outbound without burning time or budget on traditional sales hires. Saw that you''re building {company_name} and thought it might be worth connecting.\n\nOpen to it?"}, "campaign_type": "linkedin_connection", "message_wait_days": 5, "followup_wait_days": 5, "connection_wait_hours": 36}', '{}', '1e52138a-7f3e-4e97-9e56-40a4c3d08d7a', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
